    <svcsubsec id="x08259111">
        <title>BODY AND TRAILER STOP LIGHT RELAY</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
            <title>CIRCUIT FUNCTIONS</title>
            <para>When the brake pedal is applied a signal from the ESC will energize the body and trailer stop light
                relay. The energized relay provides battery voltage to body builder turn/stop connector (4460) and
                (4460A) and the trailer socket.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
